summary: A non-ENB Noir (Black and White) for best performance
descriptionHtml:
Hi! I really like ( [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/4746442]joshezzell[/url] [size=2]ENB Noir) http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26327/? But found skyrim hard to run smoothly in some instances while running ENB Noir so! here is an Sweet FX alternative for best performance.. 

[/size]Install: Place files in your skyrim installation directory where your skyrim executable is located..

Uninstall: Remove files from your skyrim installation directory..
